Name: Northlander Polearm Billet
Desc: Weapon forging material. Can be used to forge 4-star polearms. \nPhilosophers believe marble has the potential to be sculpted into a beautiful statue. Likewise, these billets have the potential to become something greater.
SourceList: Reward for completing Trounce Domain Challenge in Mondstadt, Liyue, or Inazuma, or the Dominator of Wolves Challenge
